						               													<description>In Godrealm, take control of one of four colossal Titans of earth, wind, water, or flame as you lead your armies in violence and conquest!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Godrealm is an arena combat-and-control game for 2 to 4 players taking the role of opposing gods to command colossal champions of their chosen element. Through turn-based warfare, players battle using both their avatar and gathered armies in an effort to vanquish other champions and claim dominance over the lands of the Godrealm!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players simultaneously select three cards from their hand that will dictate which actions they take on their turn during the three phases of the round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On a player's turn, they will play one of their actions (in phase order), consisting of moving, attacking with avatars or armies, or using special abilities. Each avatar has its own special ability. Special actions can also be acquired through board exploration.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players earn Victory Points by achieving control over the Pillar of Power in the center of the map, defeating enemy avatars, and capturing enemy home territories. After a player achieves a Victory Point threshold (that varies based on player count), that player is crowned as the new ruler of the Godrealm.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
